Current tasks
=============

Testing
=======
* Проверить воспроизводимость результатов измерений
* Проверить на граничные значения входных данных (аргументы, ...)
* Проверить в некорректных режимах: несколько ветвей на ядро.
* Проверить на разных библиотеках стандарта MPI, с разными компиляторами.
* Test mpiperf on different compilers: gnu, intel, oracle, pathscale. 
* Test mpiperf on different MPI libraries: MPICH2, Open MPI, Intel MPI, MVAPICH2.

Milestones
==========

Milestone 0.0.1 (Initial version)
=================================
* Benchmarks for all MPI 2.2 collectives.
* Total and per process reports.
* Examples of reports.

Milestone 0.0.2
===============
* autoconf: check for openmpi functions (scatter_block)
* Report time of first and second call of routine (test for late initialization)
* Add benchmarks for non blocking collectives.
* Add benchmarks without synchronization of processes (alternative approach).
* Implement benchmarks for point-to-point operations (according to MPI 2.2). 
* Implement benchmarks for derived datatypes routines. 
* Implement benchmarks for groups and communicators routines.
* Implement benchmarks for process topologies routines.
* Implement benchmarks for one-sided communications routines.
* Implement benchmarks for i/o routines.

Milestone 0.0.3
===============
* Add benchmarks for message rate (for collectives and point-to-point routines).
* Implement benchmarks for measuring memory consumption.
* Implement benchmarks with background noise.
